trans-unit.source: Exposes synchronous and asynchronous enumeration of the files for the vm.
trans-unit.target: Exposes synchronous and asynchronous enumeration of the files for the vm.

trans-unit.source: If true, performs a recursive list of all files of the vm.
trans-unit.target: If true, performs a recursive list of all files of the vm.

trans-unit.source: If false, returns only the files at the vm directory root.
trans-unit.target: If false, returns only the files at the vm directory root.

trans-unit.source: The ODATADetailLevel object can be used to set a select clause, filter clause, and expansion clause.
trans-unit.target: The ODATADetailLevel object can be used to set a select clause, filter clause, and expansion clause.

trans-unit.target: For listing VM files, the following table lists the property names that can be used in the <codeEntityReference>P:Microsoft.Azure.Batch.ODATADetailLevel.SelectClause</codeEntityReference> that correspond to the appropriate <codeEntityReference>T:Microsoft.Azure.Batch.ITaskFile</codeEntityReference> properties.

trans-unit.target: A collection of BatchClientBehavior instances that are applied after the CustomBehaviors on the current object and after the behavior implementing the DetailLevel.
